\frac{1}{3}\times\frac{2}{3}+\frac{1}{3}\times\frac{1}{3}\times\frac{1}{3}\times\frac{2}{3}+\cdots=\frac{2}{9}\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}9^{-n}=\frac{2}{9}\times\frac{1}{1-\frac{1}{9}}=\frac{2}{9}\times\frac{9}{8}=\frac{1}{4}
P(RS \; or\;  RRRS \; or\; ......)=P(RS)+P(RRRS)+...
P\left(RRRS\right)=P\left(R\right)\times P\left(R\right)\times P\left(R\right)\times P\left(S\right)
